Since becoming controversial when she began blogging as The Veiled Gal where she provides beauty, fashion, health, and lifestyle posts, many people have been criticizing her blog.

It's my personal blog where I offer insight and inspiration on a variety of subjects.  I’ve received numerous “hate” mail and even been executed on the internet by some uninformed people. However, for every 20 letters of hate, I received 10 encouraging and sincere appreciation for my blog.  So to all the haters, I just say:
